##com.greenbeansoft.CheckmarkCalendarLite
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
Checkmark Calendar is a multipurpose calendar solution and part of our personal organizer suite of products in Android platform.
The product enables user to access calendars created by Google Calendar, or by our own product
Checkmark To Do List Manager.
Tablet is now fully supported
The calendars can be viewed individually or in combination by generating an integrated calendar.
Checkmark Calendar provides Day, Week and Month viewing formats.
Each viewing format is customizable according to user's preferences.
Week viewing format supporting both 5day (work day) and 7day (whole week) views.
Each Calendar is color coded to distinguish from each other.
User can add/edit Google Calendar event or Checkmark To Do List Manager Task/Checklist directly from Checkmark Calendar.
Free version allows user to view events in previous month, current month and next month.
Full version has no limitation.
Native Google calendar color is inherited and can also be overridden.
Build in search function to find your tasks/events very easy.
Calendar can be viewed in different style based on calendar type(Country Holidays, religious Holidays, etc).
Please visit http://calendar.greenbeansoft.com/calendarstyle for supported calendar style.
Build in Moon Phase Calendar to display moon phase of any day graphically(Pro version) Simple, ergonomic design and intuitive navigation.
Users can perform most of their operations by clicking or long click UI elements.
4x1 week view widget and 4x4 month view widget support(pro only).
The app is also Android PAD ready.
Multiple languages support: English,  Deutsch, italiano, Nederlands, polski,, svenska, norsk, dansk,  and suomi.
resizeable widget DO NOT move it to sd
To learn more, please visit our Checkmark Calendar web site: calendar.greenbeansoft.com
Recent changes: 1.
Fixed Force Close issue for Android OS 4.0 or higher.
Added an option in settings window to show or hide week number.
Fixed a event display issue in Month view.
Fixed a month display issue in 4x1 widget header.
Content rating: Everyone
##com.gau.go.launcherex.gowidget.calendarwidget
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
GO Calendar widget brings the calendar and the agenda to your home screen.
It was designed to make it more simple and faster to work with your calendar.
Two different views (month and agenda) give you a good overview to your upcoming events.
It also supports showing Chinese Lunar and Moon phase.
Compare to the traditional calendar widget, it supports switching between months by flipping like a real calendar.
Moreover, like other GOWidgets, theme is also supported.
To make it work, you must install the latest version of GO Launcher EX which is the most popular home launcher app in Android Market.
Available Size: 4x3 2x2 Actions:
View month
View agenda
Flip
Add agenda
View Chinese Lunar
View Moon phase
How to add GOWidget to your home screen
Press the GOwidget option and choose the widget you like.
Make sure you have enough room for the widget.
Keywords: GOWidget, GO Launcher EX, Calendar, Agenda, Lunar, Moon Phase
Recent changes: 1.
(Improve) The 43 Style can show the Schedule in the 4.0 ICS.
(Improve)The schedule list can show the tasks in 30 days.
Content rating: Everyone

##uk.co.olilan.touchcalendar.trial
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
See your whole calendar at a glance.
No more flipping between different calendar views.
Touch Calendar does it all from one zoomable and scrollable view.
Rated 95% by reghardware.com ( http://goo.gl/vlIa5 ) and 9/10 by WIRED ( http://goo.gl/lLPoa ).
Touch Calendar works with Google Calendar and any other calendars your phone supports, and the app features calendar search and custom repeating events
biweekly, bimonthly).
For home screen widgets or to support the developer, please purchase the full version of Touch Calendar.
Touch Calendar is easy to use:
doubletap or pinch zoom to zoom in
tap an event to see its details , then press MENU to edit or delete it
tapandhold on a date to add a new event
touch to scroll as much as you want, both forwards and backwards
jump to today, or to any date from the menu
earch by pressing your phone search button or from the menu
calendar s  set the font size and default zoom level from the Settings
home screen widgets (buy the full version) Zoom and scroll your calendar with complete freedom
Note: Text colour for events comes from the calendar colour.
Set up different colours for events in Google Calendar and they'll appear in Touch Calendar automatically.
Permissions: read and write calendar are required of course, and also read contacts so guests can be invited to events.
Recent changes: 1.0.19:
Autocomplete now works in the Guests field.
Note: making this work required adding the "access contacts" permission to the app
Fix for several force close issues
Compatibility changes for ICS 1.0.18:
Visual update: new cleaner look
New colour scheme: blue and white  Zoom buttons now off by default on Android 2.0 (can be turned back on in settings)
Fix for goto wrong date issue  Fix for allday bubbles sometimes not displaying properly
Content rating: Everyone
##dk.alxb.calendardroid
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
Calendar Droid is a calendar app that let you see your synced calendars on your phone.
Works with all synchronized calendars like Google Calendar, Exchange, Facebook, etc.
The philosophy behind this app is a calendar that is easy to use, clean, intuitive, and highly customizable.
Calendar Droid is still in BETA.
This means the app is actively being developed and improved.
This also means that I would really like some feedback from you.
Please email me with your suggestions, experiences, or bugs.
I cannot respond in comments.
Please remember to rate Calendar Droid.
The more people using it the more it will be improved.
Help spread the word.

FEATURES: Month View / Week View / Day View / Agenda View / Weeks View View eventsAdd/edit events Some settings to customize BEFORE RELEASE: Removal of all bugs Selection of shown and synchronized calendars Your suggestions tons now off b
FUTURE PAID VERSION (Probably around 23 USD): Advanced recurrence rules (biweekly etc) Copy paste of events Change calendar colors Search events Color themes Widgets on of shown
PERMISSIONS:  FULL INTERNET ACCESS Calendar Droid is in BETA and I need all the feedback I can get from you. nt
The internet permission is used to submit anonymous error reports if the app crashes.
No personal information is transmitted.
The permission will be removed when the app is released as version 1.0.
READ CONTACT DATA If you have any guests (or attendees) on an event and you have that person in your contacts the app will read information from that contact and show it when viewing an event. d
The contact picture will show up and then clicked will take you to the default "contact clicked" scenario.
I know this permission looks bad together with internet access but I do not store nor send any contact info.
Only contacts that are guests to viewed events are read.
READ CALENDAR EVENTS This should be obvious.
ADD OR MODIFY CALENDAR EVENTS AND SEND EMAIL TO GUESTS
Read the description again and see if you can spot what this is used for ;)
Again, this should be obvious. sh
Calendar Droid needs to change your calendar events.
Sending emails to guests is done when putting email addresses in the "guest" box when creating an event.
7 Force close bugs removed (stabilizing)  0.8.0 RC1 Major update. ND

Add/edit event window with ICS style  Week/Day View horizontal swype/scroll rewrite  Attempt at speed improvements  Date Spinner when selecting dates  Delete event from "long press menu"  Agenda load more events by pressing footer  tons now o

##pregnancy.disc.app

Pregnancy Disc, your journey begins here.
The most extensive pregnancy tracker in the market.
A pregnancy app for week by week baby tracking that allows for comprehensive tracking of your pregnancy.
The application tracks important milestones in this wonderful journey you and your partner go through.
Information you can expect to have is when the baby heart starts beating, when he or she will start sucking her thumb, and when she or he will start to turn in preparation for birth. le
Also, great ultrasound 2D and 3D images allow you to impress the stages of your pregnancy.
Unique features inside this application: Features:
Pregnancy disc, also known as pregnancy wheel or wheel calculator predicts the dates of your pregnancy, week by week, that way you'll know what the dates are in each pregnancy week and vice versa.
The disc enables you to plan accordingly your medical appointments, flights, baby showers and so on.
42 weeks info that provides a wealth of information about your pregnancy, week by week, at your fingertips.
Everything you need to know prior to birth for you and your partner.
Great ultrasound 2D and 3D images.
Calendar integration, creating private notifications within your mobile calendar (e.g.
Outlook, Gmail, Yahoo etc.).
That way when ever you'll set an appointment in your calendar you'll know what pregnancy week you're on.
Pregnancy glossary  An alphabetic list of basic pregnancy terms that are often used in doctor offices, patient leaflets and among health care professionals. ac
Pregnancy Tips.
Baby Names.
To use the pregnancy disc, simply provide one of the following: (i) The date of your last menstrual period, (ii) Your conception date (iii) The expected due date.
For any question or app related issue, please contact HipoAppsgmail.com
Recent changes: Ultrasound Gallery with 2D and 3D images.
Yellow background for unknown gender.

##com.acrea.doodle.android
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
The official Android app of Doodle, the popular online scheduling service.
It supports the most frequent Doodle use cases:
Create polls for scheduling events
View and participate in a poll
View your calendar during participation
Edit and delete entries in a poll
Invite users from your address book
Close polls
Add/Delete comments
Keep the overview of all your polls by using a (free) MyDoodle account QUICK MANUAL:
Use a (free) MyDoodle account for maximising the value of the app
Use your phone's menu button to access additional functionality like editing participations or closing polls

In the settings, you can choose whether the calendar names should be shown

DATA PROTECTION STATEMENT: The data that is displayed from your phone's calendars stays on your phone and is not sent anywhere.

This app has been built with the help of Petr Koukal.
Recent changes:
Support for the calendar access in Android 4.0
Fixed a potential crash during authorization

##com.joeprogrammer.blik
##\APPLICATION\PRODUCTIVITY\ desc.txt
Why use a boring calendar widget that only has words when a cool picture can tell the story
Use the Blik Calendar Widget and you'll have a great companion to your Calendar app.
Blik reads your calendar and automatically picks a picture for each event that describes it without words.
The picture is shown, along with the start time and an important word from the event text so that you can see what's coming up on your calendar.
You end up with a quick visual guide to your upcoming events.
Your calendar has never been easier to "read".
The free/trial version of Blik comes with 350 pictures and 700 keywords rules.
The Pro version unlocks another 300 keyword rules so that your calendar events are matched up to pictures even better.
You can create your own keyword rules for single calendar events in the free/trial version and in the Pro version you can create your own keyword rules that apply to all your calendar events.
Check out the Blik Settings screen under the Help section for helpful Tips (like how to subscribe to a holiday calendar).
English only for now.
Keywords: calendar, agenda, birthday, holiday Known issue(s): > Latest update has experimental support for Android 4.0 (ICS).
Report problems to supportjoeprogrammer.##com.
Facebook events may be displayed with incorrect starting times.
Use Blik Advanced Setting value to manually adjust the display for all Facebook start times.
Facebook declined events will still show up.
Larger widget sizes can result in outofmemory crashes.
Daylight Savings Time change.
If your phone is showing events off by an hour, you may need to power it down and reboot for it to pick up the time change from your cell provider.
Important Note
If you are having problems with your calendar events not syncing, go to http://android.joeprogrammer.com/blikhelp/synchelp.html for information and instructions on how to correct the problem.
Recent changes: 2.4.9 > fix for Presidents Day keyword > menu item added to My Events screen 2.4.8 > EXPERIMENTAL support for Android 4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich) added.
To report problems on ICS, send email to supportjoeprogrammer.com with details.
New look to the My Events screen.
Bugfix: possible crash when tapping events on the My Events screen fixed.
Bugfix: widget will now refresh if the time, date, or timezone is changed.
Five new pictures added; five updated; more keywords added.
Content rating: Everyone

##com.kodeninjas.ultimatebudgets
##\APPLICATION\FINANCE\ desc.txt
ULTIMATEBUDGETS is a powerful personal finance manager.
It will help you plan your budget, manage your expenses, bills and analyse your finances through a vast array of features.
For a complete overview and tutorial, check out the website here: http://ultimatebudgets.kodeninjas.com ULTIMATEBUDGETS is unique in contrast to most personal finance managers available.

It has been designed around the concept of 'Virtual Envelopes' an extension of the envelope budgeting principle to assist with the growing complications of budgeting in a ever increasing 'cashless' world.
In addition to this, ULTIMATEBUDGETS also considers your personal income details as a critical data input.
You cannot plan, budget or manage funds you do not have, and this information is fundamental to effective budgeting.
Envelope Budgeting is a simple and organized method of saving money for budgeted expenses and allowances.
It is based on the theory that as you earn income, you put aside a specific amount into each budget envelope to cover the expense amount when it is due.
Unfortunately this concept in practice can also complicate the process of finance management.
When funds are physically taken out of secure accounts and disseminated amongst many budget envelopes, it can create difficulty when one is looking for a quick consolidated view of all funds.
ULTIMATEBUDGETS uses Virtual Envelopes, whereby envelope containers are used to organize your budget amounts only from a logical perspective.
Physically, all funds still remain in the account the envelopes are linked to.
ULTIMATEBUDGETS can then track and manage how much exists in accounts, plus what portion of this is assigned to any linked Virtual Envelopes.
This provides a holistic view of real world funds while retaining all the fundamental benefits of envelope budgeting.
ULTIMATEBUDGETS is not just an Envelope Budgeting tool.
It's a full featured personal finance manager that compares in functionality to most popular Desktop and Web Based personal finance applications.
The features are to numerous to mention here.
Check http://www.ultimatebudgets.kodeninjas.com for a complete overview.
A fundamental requirement in personal finance is the effective tracking of all transactions.
This is often cumbersome via Desktop and Online finance systems as transaction data must be stored until you next have access to the system.
This leads to incorrect updates, or worse, no updates at all
This quickly creates poor data quality and as a result, poor personal finance management.
With ULTIMATEBUDGETS you have your personal finance manager with you at all times, right there on your phone
You can enter transactions as they occur with no requirements for Internet access and no need to remember your daily transactions till you get home.

NOTES: What mobile carriers do you support
US: AT&T, Sprint, TMobile, Verizon UK: BT, Orange, O2, TMobile, 3, Vodafone (more coming soon) How does it work
vInbox provides you with voicemail and text transcriptions of your messages by taking your missed calls in place of your regular voicemail service.
If at any time you decide to discontinue the vInbox service, you can easily revert back to your standard voicemail from your mobile provider.
Will vInbox use my minutes
vInbox works by forwarding your unanswered calls.

If you are on a contract this means that most of the time the forwarded minutes will be deducted from your voice plan, though you should check with your provider to see whether this is included in your contract. to
Can I use vInbox if I on a PrePay mobile plan e
If you are on a prepay plan you may not be able to use vInbox because of restrictions put in place by your mobile provider.  y
If you can use vInbox, please note that vInbox works by forwarding your missed calls, so your mobile carrier will charge you for any messages that you receive.

$$You can create events and home screen shortcuts to manage your sound profiles and more: Silence your phone at work Turn your Bluetooth on ready to connect your headset for a morning run Set your phone quiet when it's late at night and you haven't gone out Start the music player when a headset is connected Llama can also do: 4G APN Accounts Sync Airplane Mode Bluetooth Car mode GPS (before Android 2.3 only or Cyanogenmod) Haptic Feedback Kill Applications (also forcekill with root privileges) Play, pause and other media buttons Mobile Data (before Android 2.3 only) Reboot Run apps Run shortcuts Screen brightness Screen lock PIN/password Set Llama variables Speakerphone Screen on and off Screen timeout USB storage Vibrate Wallpaper Wifi Wifi hotspot Wifi sleep policy Create events based off: Airplane mode Battery level Bluetooth devices Calendar events Car mode Charging Day of the week Current locations Headset Llama variable Music playback (stock Android only, requires third party developer support) Phone start up and shut down Screen on and off Time of day Wifi networks NOTE: Since GPS is not used, the location tracking is limited to the number of phone masts in your area.
This will work best if you live in a populated area.
If your home and work are covered by the same phone masts, you can try using the experimental Wifibased location tracking.
If that still doesn't work, you can remove the enter/exit conditions to make timebased profiles.
